to recoding procedures or data cleaning. The only change we made before 
uploading to OSF was to delete identifying/personal information (e.g. Prolific 
ID, start date).  
4. “SCORE_Popper-Amit Replication_Data cleaning File” is the data file 
containing stepwise data cleaning. Each sheet in the workbook is titled with 
